title: Halo: Combat Evolved (Multiplayer/Online working)
description:

The thing is its a private server so there aren&#039;t shit load of people online but theres still plenty of people on it.

I know you will think it isn&#039;t real because of the format but try it. I promise you won&#039;t regret it.
